<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Songsan's Photo Diary</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white shadow-sm mb-4">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">📸 Photo Diary</a>
        <div class="d-flex">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#orderModal">게시글 인쇄 요청</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2" onclick="location.href='/order'">인쇄 주문 목록</button>
            <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="location.href='/post/new'">새 일기 쓰기</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row pt-3">
        <div class="col-12 mb-4 text-center text-md-start">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">나의 기록들</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">소중한 순간을 사진과 함께 남겨보세요.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        {{#posts}}
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card diary-card shadow-sm h-100" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="location.href='/post/detail/{{id}}'">
                    <img src="{{imageUrl}}" class="card-img-top" alt="Diary Image">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title fw-bold text-truncate">{{title}}</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-secondary small mb-2">
                            by {{author}} | {{createdAt}}
                        </p>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted text-truncate-3">
                            {{content}}
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/posts}}

        {{^posts}}
            <div class="col-12 text-center py-5">
                <div class="display-1 text-muted mb-4"><i class="bi bi-journal-x"></i></div>
                <h4>아직 작성된 다이어리가 없어요.</h4>
                <p class="text-muted">오른쪽 상단의 '새 일기 쓰기' 버튼을 눌러보세요!</p>
            </div>
        {{/posts}}
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-5 py-4 border-top">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-start">
                <span class="text-muted small">© 2026 <strong>Songsan</strong>. All rights reserved.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-end mt-2 mt-md-0">
                <a href="https://github.com/송산계정" class="text-decoration-none text-secondary small me-3" target="_blank">
                    <i class="bi bi-github"></i> GitHub
                </a>
                <span class="text-muted small">Built with Spring Boot & Mustache</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="orderModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="orderModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
        <div class="modal-content shadow">
            <div class="modal-header border-0">
                <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold" id="orderModalLabel">📦 인쇄 배송지 입력</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <form action="/order/request" method="post">
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-4">포토북을 배송받으실 정확한 주소를 입력해주세요.</p>
                    <div class="mb-3">
                        <label for="shippingAddress" class="form-label fw-bold">배송지 주소</label>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="shippingAddress" name="shippingAddress"
                               placeholder="예: 서울특별시 강남구 테헤란로 123" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer border-0">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-light" data-bs-dismiss="modal">취소</button>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary px-4">주문 확정</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script>
    const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
    if (urlParams.get('orderSuccess') === 'true') {
        alert('📦 인쇄 주문이 성공적으로 접수되었습니다!');
        window.history.replaceState({}, document.title, window.location.pathname);
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>